Content:: Dr.Thusitha Wijemanne is a Sri Lankan politician and a member of the Parliament of Sri Lanka. She was elected from Kegalla District in 2015. She is a Member of the United National Party.[1][2][3]  This article about a politician from Sabaragamuwa Province, Sri Lanka is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it.
